TITLE      Estimation of isomeric cross section and covariance
            analysis of 90Zr induced by deuterium-tritium fusion
            neutrons
AUTHOR     (Vandana, S.Sharma, P.Bangotra, N.L.Singh, M.Mehta,
            R.K.Singh, R.J.Makwana, M.Abhangi, R.Kumar, H.Sharma,
            S.Vala, K.Katovsky)
INSTITUTE  (3INDGND,3INDBDA)
           (3INDIND) Netaji Subhas University of Technology, Delhi
           (3INDIND) Delhi Skill and Entrepreneurship University,
            Dwarka
           (3INDIND) Homi Bhabha National Institute,
            Anushaktinagar, Mumbai
           (3CZRCZR) Brno University of Technology, Brno
REFERENCE  (J,JRN,334,7537,2025)
FACILITY   (NGEN,3INDGND) Neutron and Ion Irradiation Facility
INC-SOURCE (D-T) A deuterium ion beam of energy 185 keV with beam
            current 2.39 mA
SAMPLE     ZrO2 target (0.25 g wt., 0.25 mm thick, 99.8% purity),
            natural Al (0.06 g wt., 0.25 mm thick, 99.9% purity)
DETECTOR   (HPGE) Detector with relative efficiency >50% and
            resolution of 2.1 keV at 1330 keV gamma-ray energy of
            60Co.
METHOD     (ACTIV) Irradiation time is 1.5 hours.
MONITOR    (13-AL-27(N,A)11-NA-24,,SIG)
DECAY-MON  (11-NA-24,14.956HR,DG,1368.625,0.999940)
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-T) The total uncertainty propagated from :
            Gamma-ray intensity of 27Al
               (+/-2.00E-03%),
            the self attenuation correction factor of 27Al
               (+/-0.0088%) at 14.96 +/- 0.15 MeV and also:
           (MONIT-ERR) Monitor reaction cross section, Al
           (ERR-1) Counts under the photo peak, Zr
           (ERR-2) Counts under the photo peak, Al
           (ERR-3) Decay constant, Zr
           (ERR-4) Decay constant, Al
           (ERR-5) Weight of the sample, Zr
           (ERR-6) Weight of the sample, Al
           (ERR-7) Average atomic mass, Zr
           (ERR-8) Average atomic mass, Al
           (ERR-9) Isotopic abundances, Zr
           (ERR-10) Gamma-ray intensity, Zr
           (ERR-11) Efficiency, Zr
           (ERR-12) Efficiency, Al
           (ERR-13) Self attenuation correction factor, Zr
           (ERR-14) Counting geometry correction factor, Zr
           (ERR-15) Counting geometry correction factor, Al
STATUS     (APRVD) Approved by P.Bangotra(2025-12-18)
